            <p>
              <note>Translation: from P.Oxy. 8</note>
              Theon to his sister Sarapous, greeting. Above all else, as I enjoined upon you when with you, take care of yourself so that I may have you well, and do not be anxious about me because I am away from home, for I am personally acquainted with these places and am not a stranger here...
            </p>
